title: Transfer from West to East nordiq
body:
Where can I find to do a transfer from EU West over to EU East? 
Can anyone have a link or something?

replies.body: Transfers are currently disabled until later this month.  We're getting ready to ramp up rewards, so it will be down until after end of season.  Here's a [link](https://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/features/account-transfers-going-cooldown).  Hang tight!
